text: Gare de Moissac is a railway station in Moissac, Occitanie, France. The station is on the Bordeaux–Sète railway. The station is served by TER (local) services operated by SNCF. ==Train services== The following services currently call at Moissac: *local service (TER Occitanie) Agen–Montauban–Toulouse ==References== *Timetables TER Midi-Pyrénées Category:Railway stations in Tarn-et-Garonne
title: Moissac station
